{
  "verses": [
    {
      "n": 18,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Ne peeminneet tahs pa-\ngahjuſchas Leetas/ un ne pahr-\ndobmajeet tahs wezzas Leetas.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 19,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Rangi/ es darrischu tah-\ndu jaunu Leetu/ taggad ta iſ-\nplanks. Ka juhs to atſihfeet/ es\ndarrriſchu Tuksneti weenu Jeetu/\nun Uppes tuſschás Weetás.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 20,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Tee Swehri Lauká man-\nni gohdahs/ tee Puhti un\nStrausi/ jo es dohſchu Uhdeni\nTuſſneſſi/ un Uppes tuſschá\nWeetá/ ka es mannus Laudis/\nmannus Iſwehletus dsirdinaju.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 21,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Schohs Laudis eſmu es\ntew padarrijs/ tee teifs mannu\nSlawu.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 22,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Ne/ ka tu manni buhtu\nfanziſ/ af Jehkab! jeb mannis\npehz strahdais/ Iſrael.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 23,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Tu ne eſſi man atnehſis\nAwis tawu Dedsamo Uppuru/\nedſ ar taweem zitteein Uppu-\neem mannt gehdtiſs: Eſtew ne\nfimn lizzis kalpoht ar Ehdamo-\nppureem/ nedſ tew lizzis dar-\notees ar Wihraku.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 24,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Tu ne eſſi man Kalimuyn\nar Naudu pirziſ/ nedſ ar teem\nLaufeem tawu Uppuru apſlaz-\ninajs. Bet tu eſſi man tzzie\nalpoht zaur taweem Grehkeem/\nu eſſi man Bruhtumu padarrijs\nr taweem Noseegumeem.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 25,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Es/ es etnu tas/ kas es\nwas Pahrkahpschanaſ isdeſdu\nannts deht/ un ne peeminnu ta-\nus Grehtus.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 26,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Peeminnt mann/ lai mehs\nkohpa teefajam/ feiz man/ ka tu\nwarri taiſns buht.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 27,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Taws pirimaſs Tehwſtrr\ngrehkojis/ un tawi Mahzitaji irr\nprett manni pahrkahpuſchi.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 28,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Tapeitz warretu es tohs\nWirſneekus tahs twehtas Wee-\ntas tagahniht/ un Jehkabu no-\ndoht par Iſdeldeſchannu/ un Iſra-\nein par Neetwaschanahm.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 1,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Et nu klaufsajs mans\nKalps Jehkab/ un Iſra-\nBel/ ko es etnuu iſwehlejs.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 2,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Ta faſka tas KUNGGS\nkas tew darrijs un pataiſijs irr/\nno Mahtes Meefahin/kas tew pa-\nlihds. Ne bihstees mans Kalps\nJehkab/ un tu Ieschurun fo es\neſmu iſwehlejs.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 3,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Jo es leefchu Uhdeni us\nteem Iſtwihkuſcheem/un Strau-\nmes us teem Iſkaltuſcheem. Es\nisleefchu mannu Garru us ta-\nwu Dſimmunn/ un mannu\nSwehtſchannu us taweem Behr-\nnu Behrneem.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 4,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Ka tee falfohs ka Sable/\nka tee Wihtott pee Uhdens\nStrauteem.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 5,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Schiz faazihs: Es peeder-\nru tam KUNGAM/ un tas\ntaps ar Wahrdou nosaukts Jeh-\n"
    }
  ],
  "confidence": "high",
  "notes": ""
}
